<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/20538480">心理学学科内部怎么评价弗洛伊德的理论？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="395856" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"></div>


</div>
